<t>This document describes requirements for the provisioning of "roaming capability" for dialup Internet users.  "Roaming  capability" is defined as the ability to use multiple Internet service providers (ISPs), while maintaining a formal, customer-vendor relationship  with only one.</t></abstract></front>

